file.title: Untitled
file.preview:
Hi everyone,

We could really, really use your help to rally behind Chaunci King to help her raise the $ she needs to run her next vodka batch.  I have see this woman hustle like no one's business as part of our startup incubator and BTW her vodka is grand. She needs to match a loan to be able to make her next vodka run and putting some $ behind this woman is a real tangible way you can help. This Portland Monthly article says a lot about her journey http://www.pdxmonthly.com/…/meet-the-portland-entrepreneur-… 

Please spread the word about her indiegogo campaign. https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/miru-vodka#/
